PROJECTS

• Online Auction Application (e-Auction) – Full Stack Java Application
Developed a full-stack Online Auction Application using Java and Spring Boot, enabling users to list items and
participate in bidding.
Designed and implemented RESTful APIs for user authentication, item management, bid processing and used MySQL for
database management.

• Student Management System – CRUD-Based Application
Developed a CRUD-based desktop application using Java and MySQL to manage student records efficiently.
Utilized JDBC for database connectivity and ensured structured data storage with relational design. Focused on clean
code structure, input validation, and scalable architecture.

• Weather Forecasting – Dynamic Web Application
Developed a weather forecasting web application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, integrating a public weather API to
display real-time temperature and humidity.
Deployed on Netlify/GitHub Pages for global accessibility.

